snippet.title: Train Life | Now on Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
For the first time in railroad simulation, play as both the driver and company director! Take control of your train and travel the rails across Europe with passengers and merchandise.  

Train Life - A Railway Simulator now available on Nintendo Switch.

For news about Train Life, you can also follow us on: 
Facebook ► https://bit.ly/TrainLifeFB 
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/TrainLifeGame 
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/trainlifegame/
